data.description: Better than new craftsman in Bellaton Subdivision has been wonderfully maintained and is loaded with extras. This Isabella plan has an open living room with trey ceilings, upgraded lighting package, vinyl plank floors, a dining area with nook, a kitchen with bar area, granite counter-tops, a stone back-splash, stainless steel appliances, and under cabinet lighting and a walk-in pantry. The primary bedroom has double vanity sinks, a garden tub with a tile-surround in both the shower and tub area and includes a walk-in closet. It also has beautiful views that overlook and unbelievable private botanical paradise arrangement in the privacy fenced back yard that was built for gardening, it has an outdoor masonry fireplace with sitting area that includes an outdoor kitchen arrangement that includes a 16x15 in-laid paver patio that sits off of a 16 x15 Covered patio. Then the in-laid pavers lead you around to a gorgeous 11x11 greenhouse that all of the lady’s will love and includes an additional raised  bed for the growing season. This house has a two car side entry garage and an oversized concrete driveway, and a brick and hardi-board low maintenance exterior  Get ready to be blown away by this entertainer’s paradise.  Your clients are going to love it!!!
